title: County face Airdrie in Viaplay Cup last 16
title_page: County face Airdrie in Viaplay Cup last 16 - BBC Sport
maintext:
Ross County will face Airdrieonians in the last 16 of the Viaplay Cup.
The Dingwall side, who were unseeded for the draw despite finishing top of Group D, will be on the road for the encounter against the second-tier club.
The tie is due to be played on the weekend of 19/20 August.
